Sun Valley International  an ISO 9001-2000 School is situated in Vaishali a posh residential colony of Ghaziabad.  The proximity of the school with National Capital Delhi and at the same time providing a calm and serene environment conducive to the healthy upbringing of children is unparalleled.<br />
                      The school had been founded by Pt. Deen Dayal Upadhayay Foundation a society managed by <br />
                      a well  knit team of Philanthropists, Educationists, Industrialists and Businessmen with a vision to provide quality education of international standards.<br />
                      Sun Valley International School had started in 2003 and is affiliated to C.B.S.E. New Delhi, upto 12th Std. having Science, Commerce and Arts Streams. <br />
                      Life is like treasure hunt and Sun Valley International students hit the jackpots. Sun Valley places great emphasis on outdoor activities. Children often go on outings, interact with people and develop their emotional quotient, and do a whole lot of things outdoors that help them unearth a vast treasure of knowledge and experience, an everlasting experience that enriches their lives. And thats what Sun Valley International is all about: Seeking the treasure within, as the school aim says. These experiences help in cultivating the sincerity, diligence and prudence amongst students as per the school motto Sincerity Diligence Prudence.

